import React, { useState } from 'react'
import { useRouter } from 'next/router'
const CreateGens = () => {
    const route = useRouter();
    const [disableGenP, setDisableGenP] = useState(true)
    const [disableGenY, setDisableGenY] = useState(true)

    return (
        <div style={{ margin: 80 }}>
            Create {route.query.createGenCompetId}
            <form action="" >
                <select>
                    <option value="ประชาชน">ประชาชน</option>
                    <option value="เยาวชน">เยาวชน</option>
                </select>
                <select>
                    <option disabled={disableGen} value="N">N</option>
                    <option disabled={disableGen} value="S+">S+</option>
                    <option disabled={disableGen} value="S-">S-</option>
                    <option disabled={disableGen} value="P-">P-</option>
                    <option disabled={disableGen} value="P+C">P+C</option>
                    <option disabled={disableGen} value="U9">U9</option>
                    <option disabled={disableGen} value="U11">U11</option>
                    <option disabled={disableGen} value="U13">U13</option>
                    <option disabled={disableGen} value="U15">U15</option>
                    <option disabled={disableGen} value="U17">U17</option>
                </select>
            </form>


        </div >
    )
}
export default CreateGens
